# Photos Directory

This is the main directory for all website images.

## Directory Structure:
```
/public/photos/
  ├── hero.jpg              # Home page hero image
  ├── about/
  │   └── profile.jpg       # Your profile photo
  ├── categories/
  │   ├── sport.jpg         # Sport category cover
  │   ├── wildlife.jpg      # Wildlife category cover
  │   └── travel.jpg        # Travel category cover
  ├── sport/
  │   ├── sport-1.jpg       # Sport gallery photos
  │   ├── sport-2.jpg
  │   └── ...
  ├── wildlife/
  │   ├── wildlife-1.jpg    # Wildlife gallery photos
  │   ├── wildlife-2.jpg
  │   └── ...
  └── travel/
      ├── travel-1.jpg      # Travel gallery photos
      ├── travel-2.jpg
      └── ...
```

## Required Image: hero.jpg

Place your main hero image in this directory.

### Specifications:
- Format: JPG or WebP
- Dimensions: 1920x1080 or larger (16:9 aspect ratio)
- File size: < 500KB (optimized)
- Subject: Your best photography work for the homepage

For now, you can use a temporary placeholder image from:
- Unsplash: https://unsplash.com/
- Your own photography

Once you have the image, save it as `/public/photos/hero.jpg`
